They never met. Akbari's gone.

458
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,130
我想他是要進那棟樓里去
I think he's going inside the house.

459
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:25,460
我他媽的最后問一遍
For the last fucking time,

