Saul, a message from Javadi:

467
00:30:06,710 --> 00:30:10,100
羅斯塔米街421號屬于伊革命衛隊
421 Rostami is owned by the IRGC.

468
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:12,840
現在的住戶叫納塞林·莫勒彼
Current resident... Nassrin Mughrabi.

469
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:15,390
卡莉  布洛迪見的是納塞林·莫勒彼
Carrie, Brody is meeting with Nassrin Mughrabi.

470
00:30:15,390 --> 00:30:17,360
納塞林  那是誰
Nassrin? Who is that?

471
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,210
阿布·納齊爾的遺孀
Abu Nazir's widow.

472
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:26,410
阿克巴里為什么要這么做
Why did Akbari do this?

473
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:29,410
布洛迪曾在納塞林家住過兩年
Brody lived in Nassrin's house for two years.

474
00:30:29,730 --> 00:30:31,850
阿克巴里用她來審查布洛迪
Akbari's using her to vet Brody.

475
00:30:32,990 --> 00:30:34,760
阿克巴里告訴我你在這里的時候
When Akbari told me you were here,

476
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:36,260
我根本不敢相信
I couldn't believe it.

477
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,200
但是你還是出現了
But here you are.

478
00:30:38,390 --> 00:30:39,800
我的尼古拉斯
My Nicholas.

479
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:42,530
我完全沒想到你會住在德黑蘭
I had no idea you were living in Tehran.

480
00:30:42,990 --> 00:30:45,640
納齊爾死后我一直住這里
It's been my home since Nazir died.

481
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:48,660
我很抱歉  納塞林
I'm sorry, Nassrin.

482
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:51,070
再沒有人能像他一樣了
There was no one like him.

483
00:30:51,300 --> 00:30:52,560
再也沒有了
No one.

484
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:56,920
看得出來你經歷了很多
But I can see you have been through a lot.

485
00:30:57,570 --> 00:30:58,620
我上次見你的時候
When I last saw you,

486
00:30:58,620 --> 00:31:02,460
你像個就要上戰場的士兵
you were like a soldier going to war.

487
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,580
我現在是從戰場歸來的士兵
Now I'm a soldier back from war.

488
00:31:04,580 --> 00:31:06,450
得勝歸來
With a victory.

489
00:31:08,330 --> 00:31:10,340
根本算不上什么勝利
It's hard to see it like that.

490
00:31:10,970 --> 00:31:12,440
我失去了那么多
I lost so much.

491
00:31:13,810 --> 00:31:15,030
你的家人
Your family.

492
00:31:16,050 --> 00:31:17,540
尤其是我的女兒
My daughter, especially.

493
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:19,760
當我...
When I, um...

494
00:31:20,410 --> 00:31:22,810
當我完成任務
when I completed the... the plan that, um,

495
00:31:22,810 --> 00:31:26,560
安拉交付我的使命
Allah had set out for me...

496
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:29,690
這擊垮了她
it destroyed her.

497
00:31:33,110 --> 00:31:34,390
她試圖自殺
She tried to kill herself.

498
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:36,240
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

499
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:39,080
信念的缺失讓人迷茫
It is hard when you don't have faith.

500
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:40,580
她有信念
She had faith.

501
00:31:42,220 --> 00:31:44,400
她相信她的父親不會背叛她
She had faith that her own father wouldn't betray her

502
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,080
讓她生不如死
and make her life unlivable.

503
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:48,720
納齊爾幫你做好了思想準備
Nazir prepared you for this.

504
00:31:48,870 --> 00:31:50,930
他說只要你忠于安拉
He said that if you were true to Allah,

505
00:31:50,930 --> 00:31:52,270
你會心如止水
you would find peace.

506
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,800
你是虔誠的
And you were true.

507
00:31:55,370 --> 00:31:56,490
你也是
And so were you.

508
00:31:59,010 --> 00:32:00,250
你心如止水了嗎
Have you found peace?

509
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:04,790
有時能
Sometimes... yes.

510
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:07,710
但有時我會問
But sometimes I ask

511
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:09,750
為什么真主要帶走我的兒子
why God had to take my son

512
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:11,760
和丈夫  而留下我
and my husband instead of me,

513
00:32:13,150 --> 00:32:15,350
然后我的感覺和你女兒一樣
and then I feel like your daughter did:

514
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:17,650
生不如死
life is unlivable.

515
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:20,430
但我挺過來了
But I survive.

516
00:32:21,850 --> 00:32:23,050
我們都應該這樣
It's what we do.

517
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:25,550
對
Yes.

518
00:32:25,590 --> 00:32:26,770
我們掙脫苦海
We crawl out of the rubble

519
00:32:26,770 --> 00:32:28,480
重新振作
and we gather up the bodies.

520
00:32:36,110 --> 00:32:38,450
你為什么來德黑蘭  尼古拉斯
Why did you come to Tehran, Nicholas?

521
00:32:38,930 --> 00:32:40,520
我無處可去
I had nowhere else.

522
00:32:45,230 --> 00:32:46,590
你來這里干什么
What do you want here?

523
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:51,150
我想結束逃亡
I want to stop running.

524
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:23,740
你在這里干什么
What are you doing here?

