526
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:27,180
告訴我們你在這里干什么
Tell us what you are doing here.

527
00:33:27,180 --> 00:33:29,040
你在這里干什么
What... what are you doing here?

528
00:33:42,430 --> 00:33:43,740
蒙主恩澤
By the grace of God...

529
00:33:46,910 --> 00:33:48,540
