I am here to seek asylum.

530
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:52,640
只有在這里  我才能心如止水
This is the only place in the world that I can find peace.

531
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:18,090
你是德黑蘭的名人了  布洛迪
You're a big man in Tehran, Brody.

532
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:19,710
