538
00:35:24,460 --> 00:35:27,460
美國人的自我標榜與現實的美國
There's a wide gulf between what America says it is

539
00:35:27,460 --> 00:35:28,980
是天壤之別
and what it actually is.

540
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:30,290
你在看什么
What are you looking at?

541
00:35:30,290 --> 00:35:32,360
最新的羞辱
The most recent insult.

542
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:35,180
這是否能解釋你12月12日的行動
Does this explain your actions on December 12?

543
00:35:35,590 --> 00:35:36,870
是的
It does.

544
00:35:37,270 --> 00:35:38,490
